overview:
Founded in 1999, with corporate headquarters in Jacksonville, Florida, The Doctors Center Mobile Services is a provider of Mobile Occupational Health Testing Programs in Florida, Georgia, North and South Carolina. Our main motive is preserving safe work environments and improving existing safety programs for our clients and their employees.

Our services:

Mobile Audiometric Testing Mobile Hearing Testing Onsite Respirator Fit Testing Mobile Health Screening Mobile HAZMAT testing Mobile Drug Screening

Additionally, our highly experienced physicians and administrators will make sure that all our services keep your company in proper compliance with the latest OSHA mandates and regulations. For more details log on to www.mobilemedical.co or call us @ (904) 880 9515, (888) 932 3735.
